@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Warranty";
}

<div class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-body">
        <h1 class="display-4 mb-4 text-center">Our Warranty</h1>
        <p class="lead text-center mb-5">We stand behind the quality of our products with comprehensive warranty coverage</p>
        
        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 warranty-card">
                    <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                        <h3 class="mb-0">Lifetime Warranty</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>At Ottawa Opal Shop, we're confident in the quality of our craftsmanship. That's why we offer a lifetime warranty on all our jewelry against manufacturing defects.</p>
                        
                        <h4 class="mt-4">What's Covered</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Manufacturing defects in materials and workmanship</li>
                            <li>Prong repair and replacement</li>
                            <li>Stone tightening</li>
                            <li>Clasp repair or replacement</li>
                            <li>Chain soldering (for breaks due to manufacturing defects)</li>
                            <li>Ring sizing (one complimentary resize within the first year)</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h4 class="mt-4">Warranty Registration</h4>
                        <p>Your warranty is automatically activated at the time of purchase. We recommend keeping your original receipt as proof of purchase, though we maintain records of all transactions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 warranty-card">
                    <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white">
                        <h3 class="mb-0">Gemstone Guarantee</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>We provide a 2-year guarantee on all gemstones, including opals, against defects that may occur under normal wearing conditions.</p>
                        
                        <h4 class="mt-4">What's Covered</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Cracking or crazing not caused by impact or improper care</li>
                            <li>Loss of color or play-of-color due to manufacturing defects</li>
                            <li>Stone loss due to setting failure (not due to impact)</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h4 class="mt-4">Opal-Specific Coverage</h4>
                        <p>Opals are natural gemstones with unique properties. Our guarantee covers:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Internal cracking not caused by external damage</li>
                            <li>Delamination in doublets and triplets (when not caused by improper care)</li>
                            <li>Significant color change not caused by exposure to harmful conditions</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header bg-danger text-white">
                        <h3 class="mb-0">Warranty Limitations</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>While our warranty is comprehensive, certain conditions and damages are not covered:</p>
                        
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h4>Not Covered</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Damage resulting from accidents, abuse, or neglect</li>
                                    <li>Normal wear and tear</li>
                                    <li>Scratches, dents, or other surface damage</li>
                                    <li>Damage from exposure to chemicals, including chlorine, perfumes, and cleaning agents</li>
                                    <li>Damage from extreme temperatures or sudden temperature changes</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h4>Warranty Voiding Conditions</h4>
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Repairs or modifications performed by anyone other than Ottawa Opal Shop or our authorized partners</li>
                                    <li>Removal or alteration of hallmarks or identification marks</li>
                                    <li>Failure to follow our care instructions</li>
                                    <li>Use of ultrasonic cleaners on opal jewelry</li>
                                    <li>Extended exposure to direct sunlight or dry conditions</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row mb-5">
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-header bg-success text-white">
                        <h3 class="mb-0">Warranty Service Process</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h4>How to Request Service</h4>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Contact our customer service team to explain the issue with your jewelry.</li>
                            <li>Bring your item to our store or ship it to us using insured shipping.</li>
                            <li>Include your contact information and a description of the issue.</li>
                            <li>Our jewelers will inspect the item and determine if the issue is covered under warranty.</li>
                            <li>We'll contact you with our assessment and recommended repairs.</li>
                            <li>Once approved, we'll complete the repairs and return your item.</li>
                        </ol>
                        
                        <h4 class="mt-4">Service Timeframe</h4>
                        <p>Most warranty repairs are completed within 2-3 weeks, depending on the complexity of the repair. We'll provide you with an estimated completion date when you submit your item for service.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <div class="card-header bg-info text-white">
                        <h3 class="mb-0">Extended Protection Plan</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p>For additional peace of mind, we offer an Extended Protection Plan that goes beyond our standard warranty coverage.</p>
                        
                        <h4 class="mt-3">Additional Coverage Includes</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Accidental damage protection</li>
                            <li>Coverage for stone loss due to impact</li>
                            <li>Extended gemstone guarantee (5 years instead of 2)</li>
                            <li>Annual professional cleaning and inspection</li>
                            <li>Priority repair service</li>
                            <li>One free ring sizing every two years</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <h4 class="mt-4">Plan Options</h4>
                        <p>Our Extended Protection Plan is available at the time of purchase for a one-time fee based on the value of your jewelry:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Items under $500: $49</li>
                            <li>Items $500-$1,000: $79</li>
                            <li>Items $1,001-$3,000: $129</li>
                            <li>Items over $3,000: $199</li>
                        </ul>
                        
                        <div class="text-center mt-4">
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More About Extended Protection</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="card bg-light">
                    <div class="card-body text-center py-4">
                        <h3 class="mb-3">Our Quality Commitment</h3>
                        <p class="lead mb-4">At Ottawa Opal Shop, we're committed to creating jewelry that lasts a lifetime. Our warranty reflects our confidence in the quality of our materials and craftsmanship.</p>
                        <div class="row justify-content-center">
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block">Contact Us About Warranty Service</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .warranty-card {
        height: 100%;
    }
    
    .warranty-card .card-header {
        font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    .btn-block {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
    }
</style>
